<p>electrek：Tesla prepares production increase at Fremont factory, builds new parallel line under tent</p>
<p>teslarati：Tesla dives deep with Model Y casting redesign from Model 3</p>
<p>teslarati：Tesla Model Y vs Model 3 casting comparison shows that legacy auto’s ‘soil-your-pants’ moment is at hand</p>
<p>electrek：Tesla reveals revolutionary new wiring architecture to help robots build upcoming cars like Model Y</p>
